{"tid":1536093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自言看罷速龍8.31襲擊市民片段後精神受損 法庭前書記向一哥索償","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:58:14.000Z","uid":68738,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ae26ab689eb91602473de3e47892846fe80837","tid":1536093,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190903/large/1567505374_cb77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567505374_cb77.jpg&h=c07109b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申索人譚志輝。（戴國輝攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n警察速龍小隊於8.31當晚在太子港鐵站內襲擊車廂內乘客。高等法院前法庭書記指速龍小隊違反《警察通例》中使用「最低武力」的指引，而且他在電視中看到有關畫面後，不單發噩夢，更有後遺，不敢乘搭港鐵，懷疑自己患上創傷後壓力症候群。他今日入稟小額錢債審裁處，向「一哥」盧偉聰追討5,000元精神受創損失。<br />\n<br />\n申索人譚志輝表示，警方速龍小隊當日所使用的武力，其不合比例程度遠超朱經緯一案。他與很多市民一樣，看過無綫電視新聞片段內猶如恐襲式攻擊的殘暴鏡頭後，感到極度不安、焦慮與恐懼，情緒飽受困擾。他害怕再乘搭港鐵，不敢經過太子站，日後在花墟球場打完籃球，也不會再乘搭港鐵回家，而會改乘小巴。譚又指，他變得沒有食慾，睡覺時每每發噩夢，睡個多小時便會醒來。<br />\n<br />\n案件排期至10月16日提訊，其間譚會求醫，以證實自己精神受創。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190903/60005950?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60005950%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=KYuNOZm%2F4ip93LesI4%2B6vpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bd808c11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F60005950%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=3c0d20e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190903/60005950?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"e35f71265e165dcab111ab363a0a2f4a387fbecd","tid":1536093,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5d239143b7c17dec171696c1fb7f555242cc21e","tid":1536093,"uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"認真，我睇完都訓唔著"},{"pid":"69a8c28247524d4f89e96e8755e1be7d43b98720","tid":1536093,"uid":85965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"咁識玩👍🏿👍🏿<br />\n大家都一齊去claim爆佢"},{"pid":"71068577fe984911d0b1229e6f437851